{"tid":1762732,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【1/12去邊個好/大集合】愛丁堡集會(不反)  尖沙咀紅館  美國領事館遊行(不反)","createTime":"2019-11-29T19:43:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T16:25:17.000Z","uid":15696,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"10540642c8c451533ee6067eeb59db0d0cb068ec","tid":1762732,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T19:43:38.000Z","msg":"有冇人知1/12 有3個活動，TG人數真係完全唔夠呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩個公海得千幾人唔夠，真係想搞得成就入去出D力啦，以前人鏈遊行成碼有10000人，一傳十，十傳百先得。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nTG:<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">尖沙咀紅館遊行</span></span> <strong>(不反對通知書申請中，<span style=\"color: gold;\">30/11決定</span>)</strong> :<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/fivedemands12\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffivedemands12&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbYwKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=97ccef5f\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/fivedemands12</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">美國領事館遊行</span></span><strong> (已經獲取<span style=\"color: gold;\">不反對通知書</span>)</strong>:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/ThankYouPresidentTrump\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FThankYouPresidentTrump&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbYwKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=e514150d\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/ThankYouPresidentTrump</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">活動整合 :</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kPpah7G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkPpah7G.jpg&h=81f9dd0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">孩子不要催淚彈 集會&amp;遊行</span></strong>  </span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">(已經獲取不反對通知書)</span><br />\n<br />\n主辦方：社工爸媽自家教（江承昌 謝麗敏)<br />\n時間：10:00-10:30 ( 愛丁堡集會)  10:30-11:45 (遊行)<br />\n路線：愛丁堡廣場 &gt; 政府總部公眾活動區<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1761891/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1761891/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0oTirAk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0oTirAk.png&h=0846c0db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">感謝美國保護香港大遊行</span></strong></span><br />\n <span style=\"color: red;\">(已經獲取不反對通知書)</span><br />\n<br />\n主辦方：美領遊行 HKAA（陳雲香港自治行動）<br />\n時間：12:30 - 16:00<br />\n路線：遮打花園 &gt; 美國駐香港總領事館 &gt; 遮打花園<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1756856/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1756856/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YHWcvvR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYHWcvvR.jpg&h=d5553a42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">毋忘初心尖沙咀大遊行</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">(不反對通知書申請中，30/11決定)</span><br />\n<br />\n主辦方：思穎妹妹（連登巴 / 不可考）<br />\n時間：15:00 - 21:00 (未定)<br />\n路線：尖沙咀鐘樓 &gt; 紅館   (未定)<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">* 仍需在30/11與警方會面後決定安排 *</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去邊個 / 去哂 自己決定，呢個post只係畀details大家。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44e2850d28f9b4b841c29f7a465c5926a895f978","tid":1762732,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T19:44:01.000Z","msg":"推呢個"},{"pid":"515e9636b548137e03212f312865fda774b069bb","tid":1762732,"uid":68366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T19:44:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82f9d